<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_126_r1l24"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> als Jr vns aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von ſelen der <expan>toppl<ex>er</ex>in</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l25"><expan>ſunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wıe ſıe meyne . <expan>eıne<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den dıe ſache antreffe . an dem gerıcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l26">bey vns ʒu ʒuſprechen etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l27"><expan>etlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe das angeet <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt / vnd Jr rede gehöret VVıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l28"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> / wenn dıe <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan> ſelend <expan>toppl<ex>er</ex>in</expan> <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> ſand Johanns tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l29"><expan>ſünwend<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchıerıſt ʒu vns kombt / ſo ſol ſıe vnd dıe ſıe mıt ır brecht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l30"><expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> . ʒu vnd von vns für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd bey vns für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l31"><expan>all<ex>er</ex>meniklıchen</expan> on geuerd . geleyt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt recht bey vns nach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l32"><expan>ʒukome<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſdenn <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jr von den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den ſıe ʒuʒuſprechen </ab>
