<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l34">des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat <expan>gewonh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_126_r1l35">vnd <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> </ab>
